{"type":"app","meta":{"headers":{"x-nextjs-stale-time":"300","x-nextjs-prerender":"1","x-next-cache-tags":"_N_T_/layout,_N_T_/page,_N_T_/,_N_T_/index"},"segmentPaths":["/_tree","/_full","/__PAGE__","/_index","/_head"]},"html":"<!DOCTYPE html><html lang=\"en\" class=\"inter_b2991b2-module__9mH_6q__variable h-full\"><head><meta charSet=\"utf-8\"/><meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1\"/><link rel=\"preload\" href=\"/_next/static/media/83afe278b6a6bb3c-s.p.0q-301v4kxxnr.woff2\" as=\"font\" crossorigin=\"\" type=\"font/woff2\"/><link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"/_next/static/chunks/0t4txrvb5hy0z.css\" data-precedence=\"next\"/><link rel=\"preload\" as=\"script\" fetchPriority=\"low\" href=\"/_next/static/chunks/0bzupvr5gt3k9.js\"/><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/0pqt~8bl3ukh4.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/0q_xces_hgbgw.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/0rf542tkyur~y.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/turbopack-0~3g4cr3dnjaw.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/149wz8r9f~itd.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/0d3shmwh5_nmn.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/0vd8i5vsktir6.js\" async=\"\"></script><meta name=\"next-size-adjust\" content=\"\"/><title>ProofProcure — Procurement agreements that execute themselves</title><meta name=\"description\" content=\"Turn procurement conversations from Telegram, email, and voice notes into structured agreements both parties can ratify, fund, and execute.\"/><link rel=\"icon\" href=\"/favicon.ico?favicon.0x3dzn~oxb6tn.ico\" sizes=\"256x256\" type=\"image/x-icon\"/><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/03~yq9q893hmn.js\" noModule=\"\"></script></head><body class=\"min-h-full antialiased\"><div hidden=\"\"><!--$--><!--/$--></div><div class=\"min-h-screen bg-white text-gray-900\"><nav class=\"sticky top-0 z-50 border-b border-gray-100 bg-white/80 backdrop-blur-md\"><div class=\"mx-auto flex h-14 max-w-6xl items-center justify-between px-6\"><span class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 font-semibold tracking-tight text-lg\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 32 32\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" class=\"size-5\" aria-label=\"ProofProcure\"><path d=\"M6 16C6 10.477 10.477 6 16 6h2a8 8 0 0 1 0 16h-2\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"></path><path d=\"M26 16c0 5.523-4.477 10-10 10h-2a8 8 0 0 1 0-16h2\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"></path><path d=\"M12.5 16.5l2.5 2.5 5-5\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"></path></svg>ProofProcure</span><a href=\"/login\"><button type=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" data-slot=\"button\" class=\"group/button inline-flex shrink-0 items-center justify-center border border-transparent bg-clip-padding font-medium whitespace-nowrap transition-all outline-none select-none focus-visible:border-ring focus-visible:ring-3 focus-visible:ring-ring/50 active:not-aria-[haspopup]:translate-y-px disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:opacity-50 aria-invalid:border-destructive aria-invalid:ring-3 aria-invalid:ring-destructive/20 dark:aria-invalid:border-destructive/50 dark:aria-invalid:ring-destructive/40 [&amp;_svg]:pointer-events-none [&amp;_svg]:shrink-0 bg-primary text-primary-foreground [a]:hover:bg-primary/80 h-7 gap-1 rounded-[min(var(--radius-md),12px)] px-2.5 text-[0.8rem] in-data-[slot=button-group]:rounded-lg has-data-[icon=inline-end]:pr-1.5 has-data-[icon=inline-start]:pl-1.5 [&amp;_svg:not([class*=&#x27;size-&#x27;])]:size-3.5\">Sign in</button></a></div></nav><section class=\"mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6 pt-24 pb-20 md:pt-32 md:pb-28\"><div class=\"max-w-3xl\"><h1 class=\"text-4xl font-semibold leading-tight tracking-tight md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl\">Your procurement already starts in chat.<br/><span class=\"text-gray-400\">Now it can finish there too.</span></h1><p class=\"mt-6 max-w-xl text-lg text-gray-500 leading-relaxed\">ProofProcure turns the conversations you already have — on Telegram, email, WhatsApp — into structured agreements both parties confirm, fund, and execute. No new software to learn. No process to change.</p><div class=\"mt-8 flex gap-3\"><a href=\"/login\"><button type=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" data-slot=\"button\" class=\"group/button inline-flex shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-lg border border-transparent bg-clip-padding text-sm font-medium whitespace-nowrap transition-all outline-none select-none focus-visible:border-ring focus-visible:ring-3 focus-visible:ring-ring/50 active:not-aria-[haspopup]:translate-y-px disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:opacity-50 aria-invalid:border-destructive aria-invalid:ring-3 aria-invalid:ring-destructive/20 dark:aria-invalid:border-destructive/50 dark:aria-invalid:ring-destructive/40 [&amp;_svg]:pointer-events-none [&amp;_svg]:shrink-0 [&amp;_svg:not([class*=&#x27;size-&#x27;])]:size-4 bg-primary text-primary-foreground [a]:hover:bg-primary/80 h-9 px-2.5 has-data-[icon=inline-end]:pr-2 has-data-[icon=inline-start]:pl-2 gap-2\">Get started <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-right size-4\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M5 12h14\"></path><path d=\"m12 5 7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></button></a></div></div></section><section class=\"border-t border-gray-100 bg-gray-50/60\"><div class=\"mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6 py-20 md:py-28\"><p class=\"text-sm font-medium uppercase tracking-widest text-gray-400\">The problem</p><h2 class=\"mt-3 max-w-2xl text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight md:text-4xl\">Procurement happens in conversations. Enforcement happens nowhere.</h2><p class=\"mt-4 max-w-xl text-gray-500 leading-relaxed\">Buyers and suppliers negotiate over Telegram, forward specs by email, confirm quantities in voice notes. Then someone copies it into a spreadsheet, maybe. The result: unstructured agreements, delayed reconciliation, payment disputes, and zero auditability.</p><div class=\"mt-12 grid gap-6 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4\"><div class=\"rounded-xl border border-gray-100 bg-white p-5\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-message-square-text size-5 text-gray-400\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M22 17a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H6.828a2 2 0 0 0-1.414.586l-2.202 2.202A.71.71 0 0 1 2 21.286V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h16a2 2 0 0 1 2 2z\"></path><path d=\"M7 11h10\"></path><path d=\"M7 15h6\"></path><path d=\"M7 7h8\"></path></svg><h3 class=\"mt-3 font-medium\">Scattered conversations</h3><p class=\"mt-1 text-sm text-gray-500 leading-relaxed\">Terms live across WhatsApp, Telegram, email threads, and forwarded PDFs</p></div><div class=\"rounded-xl border border-gray-100 bg-white p-5\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-file-text size-5 text-gray-400\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M6 22a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V4a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h8a2.4 2.4 0 0 1 1.704.706l3.588 3.588A2.4 2.4 0 0 1 20 8v12a2 2 0 0 1-2 2z\"></path><path d=\"M14 2v5a1 1 0 0 0 1 1h5\"></path><path d=\"M10 9H8\"></path><path d=\"M16 13H8\"></path><path d=\"M16 17H8\"></path></svg><h3 class=\"mt-3 font-medium\">No structured record</h3><p class=\"mt-1 text-sm text-gray-500 leading-relaxed\">Agreements exist as informal promises with no single source of truth</p></div><div class=\"rounded-xl border border-gray-100 bg-white p-5\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-clock size-5 text-gray-400\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"M12 6v6l4 2\"></path></svg><h3 class=\"mt-3 font-medium\">Delayed reconciliation</h3><p class=\"mt-1 text-sm text-gray-500 leading-relaxed\">Weeks pass between delivery and payment because nobody tracks the handoff</p></div><div class=\"rounded-xl border border-gray-100 bg-white p-5\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-shield-check size-5 text-gray-400\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20 13c0 5-3.5 7.5-7.66 8.95a1 1 0 0 1-.67-.01C7.5 20.5 4 18 4 13V6a1 1 0 0 1 1-1c2 0 4.5-1.2 6.24-2.72a1.17 1.17 0 0 1 1.52 0C14.51 3.81 17 5 19 5a1 1 0 0 1 1 1z\"></path><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg><h3 class=\"mt-3 font-medium\">Zero enforcement</h3><p class=\"mt-1 text-sm text-gray-500 leading-relaxed\">When disputes happen, there&#x27;s no audit trail and no automatic resolution</p></div></div></div></section><section class=\"border-t border-gray-100\"><div class=\"mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6 py-20 md:py-28\"><p class=\"text-sm font-medium uppercase tracking-widest text-gray-400\">How it works</p><h2 class=\"mt-3 max-w-2xl text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight md:text-4xl\">From conversation to confirmed agreement in minutes</h2><div class=\"mt-14 grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-5\"><div class=\"relative\"><span class=\"text-xs font-semibold text-gray-300\">01</span><div class=\"mt-2 flex size-10 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-gray-900 text-white\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-send size-5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M14.536 21.686a.5.5 0 0 0 .937-.024l6.5-19a.496.496 0 0 0-.635-.635l-19 6.5a.5.5 0 0 0-.024.937l7.93 3.18a2 2 0 0 1 1.112 1.11z\"></path><path d=\"m21.854 2.147-10.94 10.939\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"mt-4 font-medium\">Forward the conversation</h3><p class=\"mt-1 text-sm text-gray-500 leading-relaxed\">Paste a chat, forward an email thread, or upload a document. Use the channels you already work in.</p></div><div class=\"relative\"><span class=\"text-xs font-semibold text-gray-300\">02</span><div class=\"mt-2 flex size-10 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-gray-900 text-white\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-file-search size-5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M6 22a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V4a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h8a2.4 2.4 0 0 1 1.704.706l3.588 3.588A2.4 2.4 0 0 1 20 8v12a2 2 0 0 1-2 2z\"></path><path d=\"M14 2v5a1 1 0 0 0 1 1h5\"></path><circle cx=\"11.5\" cy=\"14.5\" r=\"2.5\"></circle><path d=\"M13.3 16.3 15 18\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"mt-4 font-medium\">Terms are extracted</h3><p class=\"mt-1 text-sm text-gray-500 leading-relaxed\">ProofProcure reads the conversation and pulls out item, quantity, price, delivery window, and payment terms.</p></div><div class=\"relative\"><span class=\"text-xs font-semibold text-gray-300\">03</span><div class=\"mt-2 flex size-10 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-gray-900 text-white\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-handshake size-5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m11 17 2 2a1 1 0 1 0 3-3\"></path><path d=\"m14 14 2.5 2.5a1 1 0 1 0 3-3l-3.88-3.88a3 3 0 0 0-4.24 0l-.88.88a1 1 0 1 1-3-3l2.81-2.81a5.79 5.79 0 0 1 7.06-.87l.47.28a2 2 0 0 0 1.42.25L21 4\"></path><path d=\"m21 3 1 11h-2\"></path><path d=\"M3 3 2 14l6.5 6.5a1 1 0 1 0 3-3\"></path><path d=\"M3 4h8\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"mt-4 font-medium\">Both parties confirm</h3><p class=\"mt-1 text-sm text-gray-500 leading-relaxed\">Buyer and supplier each review and ratify the structured agreement. No ambiguity, no back-and-forth.</p></div><div class=\"relative\"><span class=\"text-xs font-semibold text-gray-300\">04</span><div class=\"mt-2 flex size-10 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-gray-900 text-white\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-shield-check size-5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20 13c0 5-3.5 7.5-7.66 8.95a1 1 0 0 1-.67-.01C7.5 20.5 4 18 4 13V6a1 1 0 0 1 1-1c2 0 4.5-1.2 6.24-2.72a1.17 1.17 0 0 1 1.52 0C14.51 3.81 17 5 19 5a1 1 0 0 1 1 1z\"></path><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"mt-4 font-medium\">Payment is controlled</h3><p class=\"mt-1 text-sm text-gray-500 leading-relaxed\">Funds are held and released automatically based on the rules both parties agreed to. No manual chasing.</p></div><div class=\"relative\"><span class=\"text-xs font-semibold text-gray-300\">05</span><div class=\"mt-2 flex size-10 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-gray-900 text-white\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-mail size-5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m22 7-8.991 5.727a2 2 0 0 1-2.009 0L2 7\"></path><rect x=\"2\" y=\"4\" width=\"20\" height=\"16\" rx=\"2\"></rect></svg></div><h3 class=\"mt-4 font-medium\">Updates flow back</h3><p class=\"mt-1 text-sm text-gray-500 leading-relaxed\">Status changes, delivery confirmations, and payment releases are pushed back to the original conversation channel.</p></div></div></div></section><section class=\"border-t border-gray-100 bg-gray-50/60\"><div class=\"mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6 py-20 md:py-28\"><p class=\"text-sm font-medium uppercase tracking-widest text-gray-400\">Why ProofProcure</p><h2 class=\"mt-3 max-w-2xl text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight md:text-4xl\">Less admin. Faster agreements. Automatic enforcement.</h2><div class=\"mt-12 grid gap-6 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3\"><div class=\"rounded-xl border border-gray-100 bg-white p-6\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-zap size-5 text-gray-900\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M4 14a1 1 0 0 1-.78-1.63l9.9-10.2a.5.5 0 0 1 .86.46l-1.92 6.02A1 1 0 0 0 13 10h7a1 1 0 0 1 .78 1.63l-9.9 10.2a.5.5 0 0 1-.86-.46l1.92-6.02A1 1 0 0 0 11 14z\"></path></svg><h3 class=\"mt-3 font-medium\">Agreements in minutes, not days</h3><p class=\"mt-1 text-sm text-gray-500 leading-relaxed\">Stop re-typing terms from chat into spreadsheets. ProofProcure extracts and structures them instantly.</p></div><div class=\"rounded-xl border border-gray-100 bg-white p-6\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-users size-5 text-gray-900\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M16 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H6a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2\"></path><path d=\"M16 3.128a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.744\"></path><path d=\"M22 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87\"></path><circle cx=\"9\" cy=\"7\" r=\"4\"></circle></svg><h3 class=\"mt-3 font-medium\">Supplier trust, built in</h3><p class=\"mt-1 text-sm text-gray-500 leading-relaxed\">Both parties see the same terms, confirm independently, and know payment rules are enforced — not promised.</p></div><div class=\"rounded-xl border border-gray-100 bg-white p-6\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-circle-check size-5 text-gray-900\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg><h3 class=\"mt-3 font-medium\">Payment tied to delivery</h3><p class=\"mt-1 text-sm text-gray-500 leading-relaxed\">Funds are released when delivery is confirmed. No invoicing delays, no manual follow-up.</p></div><div class=\"rounded-xl border border-gray-100 bg-white p-6\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-chart-column size-5 text-gray-900\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M3 3v16a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h16\"></path><path d=\"M18 17V9\"></path><path d=\"M13 17V5\"></path><path d=\"M8 17v-3\"></path></svg><h3 class=\"mt-3 font-medium\">Audit-ready from day one</h3><p class=\"mt-1 text-sm text-gray-500 leading-relaxed\">Every conversation, confirmation, and payment event is recorded with timestamps and actor attribution.</p></div><div class=\"rounded-xl border border-gray-100 bg-white p-6\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-globe size-5 text-gray-900\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"M12 2a14.5 14.5 0 0 0 0 20 14.5 14.5 0 0 0 0-20\"></path><path d=\"M2 12h20\"></path></svg><h3 class=\"mt-3 font-medium\">Works across borders</h3><p class=\"mt-1 text-sm text-gray-500 leading-relaxed\">Built for global trade. Supports cross-border settlement without the friction of traditional banking rails.</p></div><div class=\"rounded-xl border border-gray-100 bg-white p-6\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-message-square-text size-5 text-gray-900\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M22 17a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H6.828a2 2 0 0 0-1.414.586l-2.202 2.202A.71.71 0 0 1 2 21.286V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h16a2 2 0 0 1 2 2z\"></path><path d=\"M7 11h10\"></path><path d=\"M7 15h6\"></path><path d=\"M7 7h8\"></path></svg><h3 class=\"mt-3 font-medium\">No new software to learn</h3><p class=\"mt-1 text-sm text-gray-500 leading-relaxed\">Keep using Telegram, email, WhatsApp. ProofProcure works behind the scenes, not in front of your workflow.</p></div></div></div></section><section class=\"border-t border-gray-100\"><div class=\"mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6 py-20 md:py-28\"><p class=\"text-sm font-medium uppercase tracking-widest text-gray-400\">Built for</p><h2 class=\"mt-3 max-w-2xl text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight md:text-4xl\">Teams that buy and sell across borders, over chat</h2><div class=\"mt-12 grid gap-6 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3\"><div class=\"rounded-xl border border-gray-200 p-6\"><h3 class=\"font-medium\">SME buyers</h3><p class=\"mt-2 text-sm text-gray-500 leading-relaxed\">Procurement teams of 1–10 who negotiate over messaging and need structured records without enterprise software.</p></div><div class=\"rounded-xl border border-gray-200 p-6\"><h3 class=\"font-medium\">Global suppliers</h3><p class=\"mt-2 text-sm text-gray-500 leading-relaxed\">Exporters and manufacturers who confirm orders via Telegram and need payment certainty before shipping.</p></div><div class=\"rounded-xl border border-gray-200 p-6\"><h3 class=\"font-medium\">Recurring replenishment</h3><p class=\"mt-2 text-sm text-gray-500 leading-relaxed\">Repeat orders for raw materials, components, or inventory where terms are stable but execution is manual.</p></div></div></div></section><section class=\"border-t border-gray-100 bg-gray-900 text-white\"><div class=\"mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6 py-20 text-center md:py-28\"><h2 class=\"text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight md:text-4xl\">Stop losing agreements to chat history</h2><p class=\"mx-auto mt-4 max-w-lg text-gray-400\">ProofProcure turns the procurement conversations you already have into agreements that execute themselves. Start in under a minute.</p><a class=\"mt-8 inline-block\" href=\"/login\"><button type=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" data-slot=\"button\" class=\"group/button inline-flex shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-lg border border-transparent bg-clip-padding text-sm font-medium whitespace-nowrap transition-all outline-none select-none focus-visible:border-ring focus-visible:ring-3 focus-visible:ring-ring/50 active:not-aria-[haspopup]:translate-y-px disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:opacity-50 aria-invalid:border-destructive aria-invalid:ring-3 aria-invalid:ring-destructive/20 dark:aria-invalid:border-destructive/50 dark:aria-invalid:ring-destructive/40 [&amp;_svg]:pointer-events-none [&amp;_svg]:shrink-0 [&amp;_svg:not([class*=&#x27;size-&#x27;])]:size-4 bg-secondary text-secondary-foreground hover:bg-secondary/80 aria-expanded:bg-secondary aria-expanded:text-secondary-foreground h-9 px-2.5 has-data-[icon=inline-end]:pr-2 has-data-[icon=inline-start]:pl-2 gap-2\">Get started <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-right size-4\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M5 12h14\"></path><path d=\"m12 5 7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></button></a></div></section><footer class=\"border-t border-gray-100 bg-white\"><div class=\"mx-auto flex max-w-6xl items-center justify-between px-6 py-6 text-sm text-gra